  "subject": "Upgrade to Spring Boot 4.1.0",
  "commit_message": "Upgrade to Spring Boot 4.1.0\n\n- Uplift Spring Boot from 4.0.6 to 4.1.0\n- Remove gRPC and protobuf from parent (now managed by Spring Boot)\n- Add CVE overrides for drools transitive dependencies\n\nNOTE: drools-bom could be upgraded to version 10 to fix CVEs, but\n      it would require code changes and still not fix all CVEs.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: I9c2fc6ec02ae0f8c06e729515e3498a78725038d\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
